name: NEON NIGHTMARE
description:
"NEON NIGHTMARE" it's first artwork in a series of "nightmares".
Was inspired by my dreams.
You can see the bathroom and shower filled with eyes. In this way, I show the different views of society on my art. I also demonstraite the equality of sociaty, cause looking only at eyes you will not understand what kind of race a person is and what status in sociaty has...
